In the MATTER OF the ESTATE OF Donaven E. HENRICKSEN, Deceased. In the Matter of the Estate of Darlene V. Henricksen, Deceased. Sarita Henricksen, Petitioner-Appellee,
v.
Jim Henricksen, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0308 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

An ex-husband appeals from a ruling ordering him to pay unpaid child support and daycare expenses. REVERSED AND REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.

REVERSED. REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.
